0.woff2" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin="anonymous" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preload" href="/_next/static/media/Boyrun-Regular.woff2" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin="anonymous" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preload" href="https://www.facebook.com/tr?id=792405807634160&amp;ev=PageView&amp;noscript=1" as="image" data-next-head=""/><script type="application/ld+json" data-next-head="">{"@type":"Organization","@context":"https://schema.org","url":"https://www.meetup.com/aws-ro/","name":"Meetup","logo":"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/next/images/general/m_redesign_630x630.png","sameAs":["https://www.facebook.com/meetup/","https://twitter.com/Meetup/","https://www.youtube.com/meetup","https://www.instagram.com/meetup/"]}</script><meta name="description" content="This is a group for users of Amazon Web Services. We&#x27;ll cover Use Cases, Best Practices, Success Stories, Tips &amp;amp; Tricks, Cloud Computing, DevOps.We encourage discussions and networking and we will have fun while we learn new things." data-next-head=""/><meta property="fb:app_id" content="2403839689" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:site_name" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:type" content="article" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:title" content="IASI AWS User Group | Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:description" content="This is a group for users of Amazon Web Services. We&#x27;ll cover Use Cases, Best Practices, Success Stories, Tips &amp;amp; Tricks, Cloud Computing, DevOps.We encourage discussions and networking and we will have fun while we learn new things." data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:url" content="https://www.meetup.com/aws-ro/" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:image" content="https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/e/0/e/600_510303598.jpeg" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:android:app_name" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:android:package" content="com.meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:ios:app_store_id" content="375990038" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:ios:app_name" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:web:should_fallback" content="true" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:android:url" content="meetup://" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:ios:url" content="meetup://" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:web:url" content="https://www.meetup.com/" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:site" content="@meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:image" content="https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/e/0/e/600_510303598.jpeg" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:description" content="This is a group for users of Amazon Web Services. We&#x27;ll cover Use Cases, Best Practices, Success Stories, Tips &amp;amp; Tricks, Cloud Computing, DevOps.We encourage discussions and networking and we will have fun while we learn new things." data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:id:iphone" content="375990038" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:name:iphone" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:id:ipad" content="375990038" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:name:ipad" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:id:googleplay" content="com.meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:name:googleplay" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta name="robots" content="index, follow, max-image-preview:large" data-next-head=""/><script type="application/ld+json" data-next-head="">[{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Event","name":"Building with Kiro and Kiro CLI: A Spec-Driven Approach to Agentic AI","url":"https://www.meetup.com/aws-ro/events/315086654/","description":"Hey there, before your go on your vacation, join us on July 1th for a hands-on workshop with Kiro, delivered from a **Solution Architect Lead** working at **AWS (Dragos Madarasan).**\nThis hands-on workshop teaches you to leverage natural language prompts, structured specifications and intelligent automation using Kiro and Strands Agents SDK. Master five core capabilities:\n\n* Vibe Coding\n* Steering\n* Model Context Protocol\n* Spec-Driven Development\n* Agent Hooks\n\nWalk away with practical AI-assisted development skills you can immediately apply to your projects.\n**Workshop Agenda:**\n\n* Introduction to AIDLC - Overview of AI-Driven Development methodology and Kiro capabilities\n* Live Demo - Hands-on demonstration of Kiro\n* Practical Exercise - Build a prototype using Kiro with guided practice\n* Q&A / Networking - Open discussion and Networking\n\n📍 Location: Endava, UBC1, strada Palat 3E, 5th floor\n🕒 Time: 18:00\nWhat to bring:\nA laptop!\nP.S. There will be pizza!","startDate":"2026-07-01T15:00:00.000Z","endDate":"2026-07-01T17:00:00.000Z","eventStatus":"https://schema.org/EventScheduled","image":"","eventAttendanceMode":"https://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode","location":{"@type":"Place","name":"Endava","address":{"@type":"PostalAddress","addressLocality":"Iasi","addressRegion":"","addressCountry":"ro","streetAddress":"str. Palat nr. 3B, clădirea E5 - parter (Complex Palas), Iasi"}},"organizer":{"@type":"Organization","name":"IASI AWS User Group","url":"https://www.meetup.com/aws-ro/"},"performer":"IASI AWS User Group"}]</script><script type="application/ld+json" data-next-head="">{"@type":"Organization","@context":"https://schema.org","url":"https://www.meetup.com/aws-ro/","name":"IASI AWS User Group","image":"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/e/0/e/600_510303598.webp","foundingDate":"2016-07-21T06:35:35.000Z","address":{"location":{"@type":"Place","address":{"@type":"PostalAddress","addressLocality":"Iasi","addressRegion":"","addressCountry":"ro"}}},"sameAs":[]}</script><script type="application/ld+json" data-next-head="">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"BreadcrumbList","itemListEle